article_text:
A DailyMail.com headline nicely sums up the current degraded state of the 2016 presidential campaign: “Hillary Addresses Empty Room on Women’s Issues During Campaign Stop in Ohio Where She Slams Trump for Insulting Women ‘Every Chance He Gets.’ ” The corrupt dynast who is the inevitable Democratic nominee denounces the shallow vulgarian who leads the Republican field, for essentially trivial reasons. Doesn’t it get any better than this?
